9.Design a PHP script to display "Welcome" message and current date & time.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>PHP Date and Time</title>
</head>
<body style="text-align:center; margin-top:50px; font-family:Arial;">
<?php
date_default_timezone_set("Asia/Kolkata");
echo "<h1>Welcome</h1>";
echo "<h3>Current Date: " . date("d-m-Y") . "</h3>";
echo "<h3>Current Time: " . date("h:i:s A") . "</h3>";
?>
</body>
</html>
